On the shopping cart page, users can edit the contents of the shopping cart, perform operations such as selecting all/not selecting/partially selecting, and checking out. On the generate order page, users can generate orders and make payments. On the address management page, users can edit or add addresses. On the personal center page, users can view order records, address management, account management and other information. On the account management page, users can save account information or log out. In addition, users can also perform account registration and login operations on the registration and login pages.
